{"tid":711028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【三屍命案】《HKG報》稱女事主疑佔中後變極端　羅冠聰：消費死者、捕風捉影","createTime":"2018-06-21T08:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T09:10:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d85c00d62d63b329e84ae3d973a926b61b3dace3","tid":711028,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hkgpao20copy_WlesB_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhkgpao20copy_WlesB_1200x0.png&h=588ce9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前屯門發生三屍命案，女兒涉嫌於家中以刀刺死父母後，再以氦氣袋笠頭自殺，其遺書透露自己受濕疹困擾。由周融創辦的親建制網媒《HKG報》今日發表報道，引述來歷不明的網上文章，指涉案女生「疑佔中後輟學走向極端」。香港眾志常委羅冠聰質疑，報道惡意消費死者作捕風捉影的政治攻擊，怒轟《HKG報》是渣中之渣。<br />\n<br />\n《HKG報》今日發表的文章，以「疑佔中後輟學走向極端 弒父母女生是黃絲殺手」為題，引述一篇來源不明且未經考證的「網上瘋傳帖子」，內容指網民發現涉案女生是「黃絲帶支持非法佔中者」，推測女子2015年輟學，正值是佔中失敗後的落虛期，「好大理由是由政棍搞起的非法佔中令到她走向極端的思想及行為」。<br />\n<br />\n《HKG報》記者在涉案女子FB找到黃絲帶的圖片，並在報道最後以此作結：「惟可肯定的一點是，佔中害人不淺。究竟多少年輕人因此走上歧路？多少美好家庭因此而破碎？大家市民都有眼見。」<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰隨即在FB發文回應，質疑家庭倫常慘案被塑造成「佔中後走向極端」，指報道不反省現況、查探真相原因，反而惡意地消費死者作捕風捉影的政治攻擊，「簡直是無恥、人渣所為。HKGPAO是渣中之渣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/三屍命案-hkg報-稱女事主疑佔中後變極端-羅冠聰-消費死者-捕風捉影/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%8D%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-hkg%E5%A0%B1-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%96%91%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%8C%E8%AE%8A%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0-%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85-%E6%8D%95%E9%A2%A8%E6%8D%89%E5%BD%B1%2F&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=cea47ae5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%8D%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-hkg%E5%A0%B1-%E7%A8%B1%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%96%91%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%8C%E8%AE%8A%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0-%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85-%E6%8D%95%E9%A2%A8%E6%8D%89%E5%BD%B1%2F&h=ec0efa3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/三屍命案-hkg報-稱女事主疑佔中後變極端-羅冠聰-消費死者-捕風捉影/</a>"},{"pid":"8b00976606bbbc33466f38609c218c1c79832b5d","tid":711028,"uid":58552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"無改錯名 支報"},{"pid":"70f5bf79777707841e06ed4e19972eff7cfd30fb","tid":711028,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7493ecafe9b7e02a56aeb865f8644b3c94ee7757","tid":711028,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"看圖作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbcf9cac5e515588ac3f80cfbd4daf572e01606","tid":711028,"uid":156005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"香港支報作文 formula<br />\n_ _疑因佔中變極端犯事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b057648a33c2092d74f6f170df05d1904b97b7","tid":711028,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"高登報真係害人不淺"},{"pid":"9ba409632802388124d610a44be32f99af7fae1b","tid":711028,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"本身個case已經慘 仲要屈死者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  奶共奶到痴撚線"},{"pid":"646cb2baac816d21974ee3cc0bd859a6daec41cf","tid":711028,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"林過雲殺人尬一家係因為佔中啦"},{"pid":"407b41a6a8777bb338e45863a49d906ebde6fdf9","tid":711028,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林過雲殺人一定係因為佔中啦</blockquote>"}]}